test_name: UDSVERTN is the total of subquestions
short_desc: If UDSVERFC not 95-98 and UDSVERLC not 95-98, UDSVERTN must be the total of UDSVERFC and UDSVERLC
full_desc: If Q12a. UDSVERFC not 95-98 and Q12d. UDSVERLC not 95-98, Q12g. UDSVERTN must be the total of UDSVERFC and UDSVERLC
test_logic: UDSVERFC <= 40 and UDSVERLC <=40 and UDSVERTN not = UDSVERFC + UDSVERLC

test_name: UDSVERTE is the total of subquestions
short_desc: If UDSVERFN is between 0 and 15  and UDSVERLR is between 0 and 15, then UDSVERTE must be the total of UDSVERFN and UDSVERLR
full_desc: If Q12b. UDSVERFN (f-words repeated) is between 0 and 15 and Q12e. UDSVERLR (L-words repeated) is between 0 and 15, then Q12h. UDSVERTE must be the total of Q12b. UDSVERFN and Q12e. UDSVERLR
test_logic: UDSVERFN >=0 and UDSVERFN <=15 and UDSVERLR >= 0 and UDSVERLR <=15 and UDSVERTE not = UDSVERFN + UDSVERLR

test_name: UDSVERTI is the total of subquestions
short_desc: If UDSVERNF is between 0 and 15  and UDSVERLN is between 0 and 15, then UDSVERTI must be the total of UDSVERNF and UDSVERLN
full_desc: If Q12c. UDSVERNF (F-words rule violations) is between 0 and 15 and Q12f. UDSVERLN (L-words rule violations) is between 0 and 15, then Q12i. UDSVERTI must be the total of Q12c. UDSVERNF and Q12f. UDSVERLN
test_logic: UDSVERNF >=0 and UDSVERNF <=15 and UDSVERLN >=0 and UDSVERLN <=15 and UDSVERTI not = UDSVERNF + UDSVERLN
